The Dark Tower (2017)

Action | Adventure|Horror | Sci-Fi
The Gunslinger, Roland Deschain, roams an Old West-like landscape where "the world has moved on" in pursuit of the man in black. 

Also searching for the fabled Dark Tower, in the hopes that reaching it will preserve his dying world.
Director: Nikolaj Arcel
Stars: Katheryn Winnick, Matthew McConaughey, Idris Elba, Jackie Earle Haley
